Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:01.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:09.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:11.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:13.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:14.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:18.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}An incarnation of Naraku which had\nbeen split into two was still alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:21.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the legendary demon horse, Entei,\nreleased from its seal{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:24.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}now presents himself\nto his chosen rider!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:05.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to look into your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:17.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:19.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Entei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:24.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:29.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's enough outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell do I do\nwith this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:50.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not even breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:53.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It {\i1}moved....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey. Did you come back\nfrom the dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:07.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's {\i1}alive....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:21.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:53.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:03:59.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:18.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:19.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:20.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:23.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless! It's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:25.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? It's descending!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:31.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Entei's master must be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean the man-eating demon that's\nsealed up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'll destroy 'em both,\NEntei and him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So the priest is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Coming to greet your {\i1}master....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that's a nice thing\nto do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we raise hell like\nold times?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:13.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:18.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're Rengokuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,None of your business!\NJust get back in your grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:24.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am the great {\i1}Rengokuki....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:28.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only one Entei allows\nastride his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:32.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've got guts if\nyou wanna fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:45.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this! And this! And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:58.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You almost had him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:02.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll take some doing to\nget that demon horse, Entei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:07.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A human attack will have\nno effect on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:11.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am destined to conquer the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:14.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:17.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:22.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He countered it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The problem is that speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:25.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run, Entei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:38.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's hunger! I'm hungry,\nthat's why I don't have strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:41.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd never lose to a guy like that\notherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:46.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:51.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:53.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are Rengokuki and Entei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was too late. They got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Otherwise, there will surely\nbe casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rengokuki is a man-eating demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to do something fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At any rate, let's follow in the\ndirection they flew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can track them by their scent\nif we get near.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:14.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Get on.\N- 'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:15.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Bring me new apparel"?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:26.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The second he wakes up,\nthat kid starts ordering me around!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:28.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What could have happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What kind of demon are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:58.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me tell you {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The humans who were here\nare all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:02.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:04.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:07.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:10.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:14.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In time, I'm going to rule the world.\NAnd you'll be my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not a bad deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:19.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't look like you can\nconquer the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:21.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:30.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:47.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Entei! I'll give her a taste\nof my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:51.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance of Blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:54.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}horse....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:02.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's really irritating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:15.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come down.\NI'll take you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:26.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you apologize and ask me\nto take you for a wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:33.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! You'll regret picking\na fight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:39.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll show you my power\nwhich even Entei acknowledges.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:42.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I told you that\nyou don't look strong at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Kagura...\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll handle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You cocky kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:13.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Entei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:19.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Entei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:25.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:28.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Entei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm your master!\NHave you forgotten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:33.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:37.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He decides who is the most fitting\nto ride on his back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it is my power he chose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm the victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:16.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Behold! I am the rider\nof Entei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us go, Entei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:30.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Entei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you see in\na kid like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:35.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:39.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}kid....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:46.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:11:59.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:14.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Am I going to be {\i1}killed....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:20.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,by a mere kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:27.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it too big for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Save your wisecracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to get used to\nthis body quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:40.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This kid... Unlike Naraku,\nhe doesn't mind getting his hands dirty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:46.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All the people who lived\nhere were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:00.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did Rengokuki do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:00.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:02.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hoof marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:09.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:11.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's find them as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:15.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Entei's prints go in that direction,\nbut stop right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:17.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He must've flown\nfrom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean he flew\nin that direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:21.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:22.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Be careful, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:27.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An {\i1}aura....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demonic aura is\ncoming near!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:48.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that Entei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:56.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're brave, coming\nto me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's going to hit this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:11.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A barrier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's some greeting\NInuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not Rengokuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:25.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I killed Rengokuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:26.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:31.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems Entei here has\nchosen me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,after witnessing my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A mere child!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:43.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or maybe, it was for\nfreeing him from the seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the one\nwho released that demon horse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:49.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The ones who broke the seal\nwere Kagura and that baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:54.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The baby was split in two\nby the priest's spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:15:00.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ha! As if I'd die from the\nspiritual powers of a mere priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean you're that baby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am Hakudoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As you've guessed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am one of Naraku's\nincarnations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:14.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're {\i1}Naraku's....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:19.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have heard that you have\nkilled monks and priests
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:22.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in search of the border between\nthis world and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:23.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is to be found there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:28.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you like to search\nfor it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel shard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sacred Jewel shard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, is it wise to\ntalk about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no need to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The more, the merrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be grateful that I've\ngiven you that lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:48.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He seems to be telling\nthe truth about the shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:52.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I don't give a damn about\nthe next world or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:54.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but if there's a shard to be\nfound there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you can go there yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:04.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He got away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:15.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't let 'em get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll find them, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:24.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll you do now?\NKill another priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:27.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not anymore.\NHumans aren't strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:32.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I saw inside the priest's soul\nbefore he split me in two...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:36.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}was that the border between\nthis world and the next?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:40.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I saw was a world of white mist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:44.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to know more about\nwhat I saw.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which means...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:51.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:53.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Find a demon who\nseems strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:55.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:14.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see... Nothing in this area either?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:18.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. As you can see, it's\nvery peaceful here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:21.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No demon horse... and no child\nriding it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:25.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've not seen anything like that.\NI'm sorry I'm not much help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:30.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since that day, we've had\nno clues at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ever since we saw Hakudoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:37.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there've been no stories about\nattacks on shrines and temples.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:41.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, but now, I keep sensing\na strange demonic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And more than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Strange demonic aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:47.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By themselves, they're not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But their movements are wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:53.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're not headed someplace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:56.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No... It's like they're wandering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:00.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Smells yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:04.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku and Sango should be\nreturning soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:11.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:14.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But what a shock that Naraku's\nincarnation would reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the location of\nthe last Sacred Jewel shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:18.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:24.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The others are held by Koga\nand Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:30.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rest are all in\NNaraku's possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:38.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't let Naraku have\nany more of the shards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:40.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:44.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He probably couldn't sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! I can't pick up\nany scent of Hakudoshi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:52.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I don't get this thing\nabout the border{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}between this world and the next.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't there some kind of clue?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:57.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anything at all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:02.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:07.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:09.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:38.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:41.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:53.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where WERE you, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:59.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you know what would have\nhappened to Kagome if I weren't here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know.\NSorry, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what is this demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you do this, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:20.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sure got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaddya mean by\ncarried away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You chopped off his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:28.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, this demon was\nheadless from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:29.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:30.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:36.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's why it was\nso scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could it have something to do\nwith the wandering demonic aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:42.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, this was probably\none of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This one looks like it was\nkilled with a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, it was beheaded?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:51.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, but demons are resilient.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why the body was\nmoving by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:55.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then the other demonic auras...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just look at this cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:03.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whoever did it was\na terrible swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it really that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:06.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:11.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:20.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you realize that\nthis is my territory?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:33.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you.!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This brat... just what is he thinking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:56.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name is Kanta.\NAs you can see, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.29,0:23:47.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A raccoon dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:48.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An otter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.06,0:23:51.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kanta's father has been slain\nby Hakudoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:55.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we can find his body,\nwe may be able to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.13,0:23:58.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But once a body is destroyed,\nit cannot be restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:00.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry Inuyasha!\NWe may make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:04.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know, but there's a troublesome guy\nnear Kanta's old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:08.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"3000 Leagues in Search of Father"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:12.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is Tenseiga telling me\nto save it?
